1. ‚ùå Using `any` type
2. ‚ùå Using NativeWind/Tailwind - Use Unistyles 3.0 instead
3. ‚ùå Using hardcoded colors/spacing - Use theme values
4. ‚ùå Using StyleSheet.create without theme function
5. ‚ùå Using useEffect for data fetching - Use React Query
